title: DJ Silviomanuel - Alternate Ends of a Day 2009 DadaDj
description:
Another 2 Mixes by DJ Silviomanuel, only this time they are a little bit different. They are meant to be Ambience mixes, a little bit Ambient-ish and dub-ish but also very suitable for having a fine background music or even a quality listening experience in the form of a musical landscape, trips through different moods, times, colours, feelings. the sound will guide you wherever you want to go. they are psychedelic without being goa, just fine music that will feed your soul. mixed with sounds that would not fit together at first sight but will at first listening. 
There are no tracklists, only some names of the interpreters:
